+# Infrastructure Setup
+
+This stack provides:
+- PostgreSQL 16
+- Portainer CE (with self-signed HTTPS)
+- Your App container
+
+## Run
+```bash
+docker compose up -d
+```
+
+- App: http://localhost:8000
+- Portainer: https://localhost:9443
+- PostgreSQL: internal (db:5432)
+
+Self-signed SSL certificates are auto-generated on first run and persist in `portainer_certs`.

